   from ads_cmsk_basic.ga_hive_db_metadata_cs t
  where(t.db_ip = '100.97.160.136'
    and t.port = '3308'
    and t.dbase_name = 'cmskoor')
     or(t.db_ip = '100.100.4.98'
    and t.port = '3308'
    and t.dbase_name = 'fopdata')
    limit 20000
